41:35.910 --> 41:37.703
Come here. I've got an idea.

41:49.256 --> 41:50.216
Straw Hats!

41:51.091 --> 41:53.761
All hands on deck for a cast-off ceremony.

41:57.431 --> 41:58.432
[grunts]

42:07.149 --> 42:08.526
I'm gonna find the All Blue.

42:12.947 --> 42:13.781
Ah!

42:14.365 --> 42:16.325
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates.

42:20.871 --> 42:23.332
I'm gonna be
the world's greatest swordsman.

42:27.253 --> 42:29.463
I'm gonna draw a map of the world.

42:33.092 --> 42:33.968
I...

42:42.226 --> 42:44.687
am gonna become
a brave warrior of the sea!

42:45.187 --> 42:46.313
[laughs]

42:49.108 --> 42:50.109
This is it, crew.

42:53.529 --> 42:54.530
The Grand Line.

42:57.157 --> 42:59.868
Nothing's gonna stand in our way!

42:59.868 --> 43:01.829
Yeah!

43:01.829 --> 43:05.291
Whoo!

